metadata.name: ARC LVCY GT
metadata.description:
ARC Lvcy GT: A front-engined hypercar designed to achieve the highest possible speed on the track. The predecessor of the ARC Lvcy Speedster.

Driven by a legend, and became as such...

ARC Lvcy GT Specifications:

Engine: 6.8L twin-turbocharged V8
Power: 1593 HP, 1190 kW, 1750 Nm
Transmission Type: Semi-Automatic
Gear Box: 7 Speed
Drive Type: AWD
Top Speed: 570 kph
0-100 kph: 2.1 sec

Lenght: 4755 mm
Widht: 2096 mm
Height: 1180 mm
Seating Capacity: 2
Ground Clearence (Laden): 105 mm
Wheel Base: 2960 mm
Kerb Weight: 2037 Kg

Designed by MELIK ARICI
